Class SlideVideo

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class SlideVideo
extends javafx.scene.layout.Pane
    SmartTrolley

    A Wrapper for spoon's videoHandler that we purchased. It matches our protocols for elements that appear in slides in that it extends a type of node and positions it's self in its parent.

    Version:
    V1.0 created: 27/05/2014
